[idchoi2-blog]: https://medium.com/@idchoi2/javascript-%EB%8F%84%ED%98%95-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%AC%EA%B8%B0-html-vs-svg-vs-canvas-%EC%84%B1%EB%8A%A5-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90-9e1ce2396fcd

